name: Haiku-Port-Games
tagline: A repository for porting games to Haiku.
body:
Haiku-Port-Games
==============

What is Haiku-Port-Games?
=======================
It is a repository for porting games to Haiku.

Want to port a game to Haiku?
=============================
Send a request to the administrator and tell them about your planned port. The game that you're porting must be released under the GNU GPL, or other compatible licenses.

Cloning this repository.
========================
This is currently under construction.

Want to download the source code? Click on the .tar.gz and .zip buttons above!
